{"tid":919832,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾眼鏡鋪","createTime":"2018-11-28T10:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T09:33:27.000Z","uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8babea74f2312cfe9f4f23b24ca553ae6abff4c5","tid":919832,"uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"半年黎換左三次架<br />\n<br />\n貪平 橫店眼鏡都係果款 咁咪走上去銅鑼灣d眼鏡樓上鋪 果間咩眼鏡夢工場 <br />\n<br />\n第一次由粗框眼鏡架 轉 玩金屬框架 但好幼 但真係好撚型 380架+580鏡片 屌你老味 用左唔夠一個月 個架比我屎忽一野坐斷左 之後用aa膠痴左6-7次都唔係辦法 <br />\n<br />\n最後又去番間鋪 佢話無得救 叫我間番同款既架 咁好啦 屌你老母 3個月後又爛撚左 有一日 無啦啦成個鏡片跌左落黎 之後佢叫我跟番個鏡片型狀簡 仲要迫9我買display <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我走撚左落去 下面果簡 咩直銷工場 簡個隻架 有新架<br />\n<br />\n屌你啦 以前眼鏡88買粗框眼鏡 用左2年都無事 呢d架真係垃圾 不過塊鏡片有牌子 反而好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da004d966bd00eeefdf7fd7e0c68cfbd5e42a85","tid":919832,"uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad1c1e00cdee7451c37266d67ffc811631886358","tid":919832,"uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:56:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f79f60b7afbb0f8fd547f95a44ec7e470a395bc3","tid":919832,"uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:58:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"366bff6533e5c2ac437b3a236cecba7710d88516","tid":919832,"uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1412a5d6d33e0bd433607e7eca31ee9296d8b6f","tid":919832,"uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:49:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"716a67b741cae50da4805265a966f4f6844852f8","tid":919832,"uid":6248,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"用左唔夠一個月 個架比